PRIVACY POLICY

This extension does not collect, store, or share any personal information from users.
All data, such as bookmarks and settings, is processed locally within the user's browser
and is not transmitted to any external servers. We prioritize user privacy and ensure
that no user data is collected, analyzed, or shared with third parties. If you have any
questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, feel free to contact us.

